latestPosts.caption:
Cypress Hill 💨
Introducing your #RRUOR25 Artists! 🏕️🍄🔊
Today, we’ve got @CypressHill!👇

Cypress Hill shifts culture. The South Gate, California rap group championed cannabis before it became fashionable, ushered in a genre-shifting sonic tapestry, performed thousands of shows at a time when rappers were having a hard time getting booked for live gigs, & helped pave the way for rappers to use Spanish in their rhymes. Along the way, Cypress Hill earned a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame, sold over 9 million albums, & was nominated for three Grammy Awards.

Which songs are you stoked to hear LIVE?🎙️
